         <t:div type="bibliography">
            
            <t:listBibl type="editions">
               <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/BL5NWGBV"><seg type="webpage"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:MgWebsite"/><title level="a">መልክአ፡ ጉባኤ፡ Malkǝʾa gubāʾe</title><author><t:forename>Augustine</t:forename><t:surname>Dickinson</t:surname></author><date>2020</date><note type="accessed">2024-09-24</note><note type="url">https://malkeagubae.com/</note></t:bibl>
            </t:listBibl>
            <t:listBibl type="secondary"><t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/C5C5HWNS"><seg type="bookSection"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Oudenrijn1960Stabat"/><title level="a">ሰላም፡ ለጥንተ፡ ላሕኪ። Ein Aethiopisches Stabat Mater</title><title level="m">Atti del Convegno Internazionale di Studi Etiopici (Roma, 2-4 aprile 1959).</title><title level="s">Accademia Nazionale dei Lincei</title><author><t:forename>M.</t:forename><t:surname>van den Oudenrijn</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Roma</pubPlace><publisher>Accademia Nazionale dei Lincei</publisher><date>1960</date><series><t:title level="s">Accademia Nazionale dei Lincei</t:title><t:biblScope unit="volume">357, Problemi attuali di scienza e di cultura, 48</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="page">297-322</biblScope><biblScope unit="volume">357, Problemi attuali di scienza e di cultura, 48</biblScope></t:bibl></t:listBibl>
         </t:div>
         <t:div type="edition" xml:lang="gez">
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="malke">
               <t:lg type="stanza" n="1">
                  <t:l n="1">ሰላም፡ ለጥንተ፡ ላሕኪ፡ በቤተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልድ፡ አመ፡ ኀወጸኪ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="2">ዜና፡ እምዜና፡ ኢዮብ፡ ዘየአኪ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="3">ኦእም፡ እመ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ መላኪ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="4">ተማሕፀንኩ፡ በብካይኪ፡ ወበዘውዕየ፡ ከርሥኪ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="5">ከመ፡ ትባልሕኒ፡ እምልሳን፡ ሐዋኪ፨</t:l>
               </t:lg>
               <t:lg type="stanza" n="2">
                  <t:l n="1">በሑረትኪ፡ እምቤተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልደ፡ ነጐድጓድ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="2">ውስተ፡ ቀራንዮ፡ ዐጸድ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="3">ከመ፡ ትነጽሪ፡ በግዐ፡ ዘአበጥዎ፡ አይሁድ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="4">ተማሕፀንኩ፡ በክባይኪ፡ ወበላሕኪ፡ ክቡድ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="5">እምገጸ፡ ሐመርየ፡ ይዝሐን፡ ዘሐዘን፡ ሞገድ፨</t:l>
               </t:lg>
               <t:lg type="stanza" n="30">
                  <t:l n="1">ኦኮ፡ ዘእክል፡ ነጊረ፡ ላሕኪ፡ ጥንቁቀ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="2">ኀይለ፡ ሰማያት፡ ዘሆከ፡ ወዘጽንዐ፡ ምድር፡ አድለቅለቀ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="3">ኀበ፡ ፀልቡ፡ ወልድኪ፡ ድንግል፡ እንዘ፡ ትቀውሚ፡ ልጹቀ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="4">እምነ፡ ዐይንኪ፡ ጠብጣበ፡ አንብዕ፡ ዘወድቀ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="5">መቃብረ፡ አበው፡ ከሠተ፡ ወኵኵሐ፡ ሰጠቀ፨</t:l>
               </t:lg>
               <t:lg type="stanza" n="31">
                  <t:l n="1">ህየንተ፡ በከይኪ፡ ፈድፉደ፡ ወአስቆቀውኪ፡ ብዙኀ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="2">ሶበ፡ ነጸርኪ፡ በመስቀል፡ አእዳዊሁ፡ ስፉሐ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="3">ተፈሥሒ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘኢየኀልቅ፡ ፍሥሓ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="4">እለ፡ አላሐዉኪ፡ እስመ፡ ይላሕዉ፡ ላሐ፨</t:l>
                  <t:l n="5">አመ፡ ይመጽእ፡ ወልድኪ፡ ከመ፡ ይግበር፡ ፍትሐ፨</t:l>
               </t:lg>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
         
         <t:div type="edition">
            <t:div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:id="Incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <t:ab>ሰላም፡ ለጥንተ፡ ላሕኪ፡ በቤተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልድ፡ አመ፡ ኀወጸኪ፡ ዜና፡ እምዜና፡ ኢዮብ፡ ዘየአኪ።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
